OL,3,CBurnham says backing him in by-
OL,4,Celection would be 'vote to change
OL,5,CLabour'
OL,7,FAndy Burnham has promised that a vote
OL,8,Ffor him in the upcoming Makerfield by-
OL,9,Felection is a "vote to change Labour"
OL,10,Fas he launched his election campaign
OL,11,Fon Friday.
OL,13,FThe Greater Manchester mayor said
OL,14,FLabour "need to be better than we have
OL,15,Fbeen" and promised to give voters "the
OL,16,Fparty back they used to know".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
