SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779523627
OL,3,CBurnham says backing him in by-
OL,4,Celection would be 'vote to change
OL,5,CLabour'
OL,7,FIn his launch speech, Burnham stressed
OL,8,Fthat there is "space to be more
OL,9,Fradical" within Labour's 2024
OL,10,Fmanifesto, including building more
OL,11,Fcouncil houses and rail
OL,12,Frenationalisation.
OL,14,FHe said: "I know there's a great
OL,15,Fresentment about inheritance tax, so
OL,16,Factually just, you know, take that
OL,17,Faway, perhaps, and look at a care
OL,18,Flevy."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
