CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779523627
OL,3,CBurnham says backing him in by-
OL,4,Celection would be 'vote to change
OL,5,CLabour'
OL,7,F"It's not about asking people to pay
OL,8,Fmore, it's just people paying in the
OL,9,Fmost unfair way possible at this
OL,10,Fmoment in time and I think there's a
OL,11,Fmuch better way of doing it," he
OL,12,Fcontinued.
OL,14,FBurnham insisted that the voters of
OL,15,FMakerfield would get "the party back
OL,16,Fthey used to know". He promised he was
OL,17,Fnot offering "more of the same" and
OL,18,Fthat, "this is a change by-election.
OL,19,FPolitics in this country, British
OL,20,Fpolitics, is tired."
OL,26,@oD@AOUyD@NOUyD@_O]zD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
