OL,3,CBurnham says backing him in by-
OL,4,Celection would be 'vote to change
OL,5,CLabour'
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FHis speech appeared to mark his
OL,13,Fambition to not only win the seat but
OL,14,Falso to challenge the prime minister
OL,15,Ffor the leadership of the Labour Party.
OL,17,FBurnham's campaign launch was attended
OL,18,Fby several Labour backbenchers and his
OL,19,Fclose friend, Liverpool City Region
OL,20,FMayor Steve Rotheram, as well as the
OL,21,Fparty's chief whip, Jonathan Reynolds.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
