OL,3,CBurnham says backing him in by-
OL,4,Celection would be 'vote to change
OL,5,CLabour'
OL,7,FPolls suggest that Andy Burnham will
OL,8,Fboost the party's chance of holding
OL,9,Fthe seat, but it could still prove a
OL,10,Ftough contest against Reform UK.
OL,12,FThe Labour MP, Josh Simons, who stood
OL,13,Fdown to allow for Burnham to run, won
OL,14,Fin 2024 by 5,399 votes, while Reform
OL,15,Fcomfortably won every ward in the
OL,16,Fconstituency at this month's local
OL,17,Felections.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
