OL,3,CBurnham says backing him in by-
OL,4,Celection would be 'vote to change
OL,5,CLabour'
OL,7,FThe Liberal Democrats unveiled
OL,8,FStockport councillor Jake Austin as
OL,9,Ftheir candidate in the election, now
OL,10,Fconfirmed for June 18.
OL,12,FAustin said the people of Makerfield
OL,13,F"deserve so much more than the failing
OL,14,FLabour government or the divisive
OL,15,Fpolitics of Reform UK".
OL,17,FOn Thursday, the Green Party announced
OL,18,Fthat its candidate, Chris Kennedy, had
OL,19,Fwithdrawn from the race just hours
OL,20,Fafter he had been selected.
OL,26,@uD@AOUwD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
