OL,3,CBurnham says backing him in by-
OL,4,Celection would be 'vote to change
OL,5,CLabour'
OL,7,FThe party said Kennedy had stepped
OL,8,Faway for "personal and family
OL,9,Freasons", but it later emerged that he
OL,10,Fhad shared posts on social media
OL,11,Fclaiming an attack on Jewish
OL,12,Fambulances in north London had been a
OL,13,F"false flag" operation.
OL,15,FA Green spokesperson said Kennedy had
OL,16,Fdeleted and apologised for the posts,
OL,17,Fbut added the party stood by its
OL,18,Fprevious statement about the reasons
OL,19,Ffor his withdrawal.
OL,26,@pD@JOUqD@HO]uD@AOUuD@LO]
