OL,3,CBurnham says backing him in by-
OL,4,Celection would be 'vote to change
OL,5,CLabour'
OL,7,FReform's Robert Kenyon ` a plumber who
OL,8,Fsaid he is "ready to take on the King
OL,9,Fof the North" in a reference to
OL,10,FBurnham's nickname ` posted a video on
OL,11,Fsocial media with Farage travelling as
OL,12,Fa passenger in his van.
OL,14,FHe said: "For me, Makerfield isn't a
OL,15,Fstepping stone, it's my home. The
OL,16,Fpeople here are my neighbours, friends
OL,17,Fand family."
OL,19,FThe current list of candidates is:
OL,21,FLiberal Democrats - Jake Austin
